com.esri.mo2.data.feat
Interface Workspace

All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseImageDirectory, DbfWorkspace
Deprecated. - the interface has been deprecated, see Content API.

public interface Workspace

Implements a Workspace which is an homogenous collection of Datasets - the Datasets are of a particular type, or enumerated by DatasetType. These are manufactured by a DataSource.

See Also:
Dataset, DatasetType
